Add support for new AMD HD audio devices. Use generic driver to detect HD audio
devices with Vendor ID AMD.

Signed-off-by: Andiry Xu <andiry.xu@amd.com>
Signed-off-by: Takashi Iwai <tiwai@suse.de>

